    <h3>CULTURE</h3>
    <h1>When Northgate’s fate went south</h1>
    <p>As a historic mall sits empty, developers and residents debate its future.</p>
  </div>
</div>
</a>
<p>Inspired by my investigative piece a year prior, I decided to use my 2022 project to continue my advocacy work.
I researched an old rundown mall right outside of downtown and learned how it exemplified Durham’s gentrification.
After completing this article, I asked my bilingual classmates to <a href="https://thepirateshook.com/2023/02/07/cuando-el-destino-de-northgate-se-fue-al-sur/">translate it into Spanish</a> so it could reach a wider audience.</p>
