    <h3>NEWS</h3>
    <h1>Early Opportunities Create Unlevel Playing Field</h1>
    <p>Sophomore Izaiah Jackson will have already completed eight AP classes by the end of the school year.
He is one of a handful of sophomores taking AP English III —a class traditionally taken by juniors.
His GPA is a 4.6.</p>
  </div>
</div>
</a>
<p>I was first introduced to investigative journalism through a 2021 partnership with the Ida B.
Wells Society for Investigative Reporting.
I published this article under the mentorship of a local journalist.
This project sparked my commitment to diversity and love of investigative journalism.</p>
